Name: assign_worker_to_task
Description: Binary decision to assign a specific worker to a task

Name: select_feature_for_sprint
Description: Binary decision to include a feature in a sprint

Name: set_sprint_duration
Description: The length of a sprint in days

Name: set_team_size
Description: The number of workers assigned to a team

Name: set_story_points
Description: The estimated story points for a user story

Name: assign_priority_to_feature
Description: The priority level of a feature

Name: allocate_budget_to_feature
Description: The amount of budget allocated to a feature's development
